Compiling
-----------
Run "make" to build the executable game488.
The executable was compiled on gl01.


Running
--------
Run the game488 executable ("./game488").


Extra Features
----------------
- Guide for block dropping - enabled by default - toggle using 'G' or from Extras menu.
- Basic Lighting - enabled by default - toggle using 'L' or from Extras menu.
- Particles break off when rows cleared (always on).
- Random colour flickering on game over (always on).


